    "updated_at": "2015-05-15T08:52:58Z",
    "body": "Did some more looking into it and when I close the window the `will-quit` event is being emitted for `app`\n\nadding:\n\n``` coffee\napp.on 'will-quit', (event) ->\n  event.preventDefault()\n```\n\nsolves the problem.\n\nIs it on windows where electron assumes that after all windows are closed it should quit?\n"
