    "created_at": "2015-05-21T02:42:50Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-05-21T02:42:50Z",
    "body": "If you run your app with electron-prebuilt the default behavior is to quit when all windows have been closed, you can set up a [window-all-closed](https://github.com/atom/electron/blob/master/docs/api/app.md#event-window-all-closed) handler to prevent this behavior.\n"
